## 8. Design system (CSS custom properties — paste into `:root` in style.css)

```css
:root {
  /* Palette */
  --blue:        #1D6AE5;
  --blue-hover:  #1558C8;
  --dark:        #0F172A;
  --surface:     #F8FAFC;
  --card:        #FFFFFF;
  --teal:        #0D9488;
  --amber:       #D97706;
  --text-p:      #1E293B;
  --text-m:      #64748B;
  --border:      #E2E8F0;

  /* Typography */
  --font:        "Inter", system-ui, sans-serif;

  /* Radii */
  --r-card:      12px;
  --r-bubble:    20px;
  --r-input:     8px;

  /* Shadows */
  --shadow-card: 0 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  --shadow-panel: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,.18);

  /* Chat bubbles */
  --bubble-user-bg:  #1D6AE5;
  --bubble-user-txt: #FFFFFF;
  --bubble-bot-bg:   #F1F5F9;
  --bubble-bot-txt:  #1E293B;

  /* Zendesk-style ticket card */
  --ticket-bg:   #F0FDF4;
  --ticket-border: #86EFAC;
  --ticket-txt:  #15803D;

  /* Escalation warning card */
  --esc-bg:      #FFFBEB;
  --esc-border:  #FCD34D;
  --esc-txt:     #92400E;
}
body { font-family: var(--font); background: var(--surface); color: var(--text-p); margin: 0; }
```

