## 9. Widget UI specs (Zendesk/Intercom pattern)

| Element | Spec |
|---|---|
| Launcher button | 56x56px circle, bottom-right, 20px from edges, `background: var(--blue)`, chat-bubble SVG icon (white), `position: fixed; z-index: 9999` |
| Chat panel | 380px wide x 520px tall, `position: fixed; bottom: 92px; right: 20px`, `border-radius: var(--r-card)`, `box-shadow: var(--shadow-panel)`, `display: flex; flex-direction: column` |
| Panel header | 56px tall, `background: var(--blue)`, bot avatar (32px circle, white "S" initial), bot name "SupportAI", green status dot (`#22C55E`), minimize + close icons (white SVG) |
| Message feed | `flex: 1; overflow-y: auto; padding: 16px; gap: 12px` |
| User bubble | right-aligned, `background: var(--bubble-user-bg)`, white text, `border-radius: 20px 20px 4px 20px`, max-width 75% |
| Bot bubble | left-aligned, `background: var(--bubble-bot-bg)`, `color: var(--text-p)`, `border-radius: 20px 20px 20px 4px`, max-width 75% |
| Input bar | 56px, `border-top: 1px solid var(--border)`, textarea (auto-resize), send button (`var(--blue)` fill, paper-plane SVG) |
| "Talk to a human" | amber/orange chip always visible in input bar area |
| Mobile (<480px) | panel goes full-screen: `position: fixed; inset: 0; border-radius: 0` |

### Accessibility
- `role="dialog"` on panel, `aria-label="SupportAI chat"`, `aria-modal="true"`
- `aria-live="polite"` on message feed div
- Send button: `aria-label="Send message"`
- Keyboard: Enter sends, Shift+Enter newline, Escape closes panel

