## 10. Analytics events (analytics.js)

Store to sessionStorage key `"supportai_events"` as JSON array. Append only.

```js
export function logEvent(type, data = {}) {
  const events = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem("supportai_events") || "[]");
  events.push({ type, ts: Date.now(), ...data });
  sessionStorage.setItem("supportai_events", JSON.stringify(events));
}
// event types: "message_sent", "bot_responded", "order_lookup", "escalation_triggered",
//              "escalation_submitted", "kb_edited", "session_start"
// Admin panel reads these to compute: deflection rate, top query strings, handoff count, avg msgs/session
```

